OL,3,CWarning after walkers cause stampede
OL,4,Cof 250 stressed seals
OL,6,FIt took place on a protected beach, a
OL,7,FSite of Special Scientific Interest
OL,8,F(SSSI), where seals were a monitored
OL,9,Ffeature, so disturbing them was an
OL,10,Foffence, it said.
OL,12,FAs a result this incident was followed
OL,13,Fup and actioned by Natural Englands
OL,14,Fenforcement team.
