OL,3,CWarning after walkers cause stampede
OL,4,Cof 250 stressed seals
OL,6,FStampede's such as this can cause
OL,7,Fserious injuries to seals. This can
OL,8,Fsee them graze their flippers and gash
OL,9,Ftheir bellies on rocks in shallow
OL,10,Fwater. Young, thin seals can even end
OL,11,Fup breaking up the ribs or their lower
OL,12,Fjaws, which the charity says can be
OL,13,Flife-threatening as they do not heal.
OL,15,FVolunteers described seeing blood
OL,16,Ftrails left on rocks following the
OL,17,Fstampede, an indication that at least
OL,18,Fsome of the 250 seals who were
OL,19,Fdisturbed ended up hurting themselves.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
