OL,3,CWarning after walkers cause stampede
OL,4,Cof 250 stressed seals
OL,6,FSue added some advice for those hoping
OL,7,Fto see seals without causing a seal
OL,8,Fstampede.
OL,10,F"Top tips: Avoid beaches with seals,
OL,11,Fstick to the cliff tops and the coast
OL,12,Fpath to avoid damaging habitats as
OL,13,Fwell as disturbing any wildlife, to be
OL,14,Ffair.
OL,16,F"Move slowly, talk in whispers, get
OL,17,Fyour binoculars out, zoom lenses on
OL,18,Fyour cameras so that that's the way
OL,19,Fyou get a good view of the seals for
OL,20,Fsure," she added.
